      • createPngFile

        public void createPngFile(java.lang.String pFileName,
                 java.lang.String pJavaFileName,
                 java.lang.String pFileDir,
                 java.lang.String pLibPath)
        Generates PNG file.
        Parameters:
        pFileName - file name which is used for creating the name for the dot and png files.
        pJavaFileName - java file name used to generate the dot file. This file should be located in the pFileDir path.
        pFileDir - directory containing uploaded files and generated files.
        pLibPath - library path in context which contains UmlGraph-5.6.jar.
